All Classes

Class Description
BusinessRules
The BusinessRules class contains the business rules specified by the bank.
DBConnection
The DBConnection class establishes connection with a database running on a local host.
GeneralCoordinator
The GeneralCoordinator class is a super class that contains the main methods of checking the user's input and sign in assets.
HomePage
The HomePage JFrame is the home page that appears to the user after successful login.
Registration
The Registration class is used to register new users by establishing a connection using the DBConnection class.
SigningIn
The SigningIn class contains some methods and SQL queries sued to sign in and to establish a connection with DBConnection.
SignInPage
The SignInPage JFrame is the main page of the program that allows the user to sign in or to register.
SignUpCoordinator
The SignUpCoordinator class is a sub class of GeneralCoordinator class, it contains methods that check the user's input from SignUpPage and a connection to the database through Registration class.
SignUpPage
The SignUpPage JFrame is the GUI for registration.
Transactions
The Transactions class contains all methods needed for transactions.It establishes a connection with the database through DBConnection class.
Transactions.type
The type enum contains all the types of transactions(Withdrawal,Deposit, and Transfer).
TransactionsCoordinator
The TransactionsCoordinator class is a sub class of GeneralCoordinator class it contains methods that check the user's input from HomePage and if it meets the business rules through BusinessRules and a connection to the database through Transactions class.
